{
  "script_id": "benfords-law",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "随手翻开一本账簿，把每个数的首位数字记下来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25056,
      "text": "你可能以为 1 到 9 出现的机会应该差不多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "但真实数据里，以 1 开头的数远远最多，几乎占了三成。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "dist",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "dist-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/dist-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "把首位数字画成柱状图，你会看到一条从高到低的滑梯。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "dist",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "dist-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/dist-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "首位 1 最高，2 次之，一路递减到 9 最矮。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "dist",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "dist-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/dist-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "这条规律叫本福特定律，广泛藏在自然与经济数据中。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-1",
      "filename": "formula-form-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/formula-form-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "首位是 d 的概率，等于 log 以 10 为底的 1 加 1 除以 d。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-2",
      "filename": "formula-form-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/formula-form-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "代进去算：首位 1 约百分之三十点一，首位 9 只有百分之四点六。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-3",
      "filename": "formula-form-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/formula-form-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "数据跨越很多数量级时，就会自然趴向这条曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "fraud",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "fraud-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/fraud-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "人们编造数字时，往往把首位平均分配，露出破绽。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "fraud",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "fraud-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/fraud-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "于是税务、财报和选举审计，都用本福特定律筛查造假。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "切换 2 的幂或斐波那契数列，蓝柱会紧贴红色理论曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "再换成均匀随机数，柱子立刻被拉平，明显不服从定律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "本福特定律说，首位数字按 log 加 1 除以 d 递减分布。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "跨量级的真实数据几乎都遵守它，均匀随机数则不会。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "benfords-law",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/benfords-law/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "一条对数曲线,竟能揪出藏在数字里的谎言，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
